As a pet owner, I want to be able to only include hotels in my search that allow pets, i cant get a sitter for my dogs so i need to take them with me.

As a hotelmanager, I want to be able to see how many rooms where booked last month, i need to be able to estimate how many emploees i need each month.

As a hotelmanager, I want to be able to responde to reviews to be able to give feedback to our customers.



